Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams embraced by a single life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are boundless beyond even the stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The dreams that we foster over time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}are waiting for the moment{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}when we come upon them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.55,0:00:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The words we exchange{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}make our hearts tremble,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and a chance meeting{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}could change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:01:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}People, no matter who they are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}as they pursue their dreams,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}have the courage to travel new paths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}As we leave behind a living{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}testament of our journey,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}the Galaxy Railways on which{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}we travel continue ever on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Everyone seeks peace of mind{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}in their lives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}But for those who drive themselves,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and spend their days in battle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}there is nothing more difficult to obtain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Emergency transmission\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from {\i1}Mother Venus No. 131.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They have a woman aboard\N{\c&He1e1e1&}who has gone into labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They're requesting immediate\N{\c&He1e1e1&}transport to medical facilities
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}at the nearest planet for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dispatch Space Defense Force,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Fomalhaut Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Incoming message\N{\c&He1e1e1&}from the {\i1}Albireo Express,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}traveling through\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the Veil Nebula in Cygnus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}An unknown group of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}intoxicated performers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}is putting on some\N{\c&He1e1e1&}sort of radical performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dispatch Arcturus Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}An unknown creature is building\N{\c&He1e1e1&}a nest on the track ring
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}at Point 309 of the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Orion Loop in Eridanus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Some furballs have gotten aboard, and are\N{\c&He1e1e1&}stuck to the passengers' hair and clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Passengers who have gotten them\N{\c&He1e1e1&}inside their nostrils
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}are showing symptoms of poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dispatch Algol Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"A Time of Tranquility"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Incredible! He's the first one out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're good at this, {\i1}Yuuki-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nah, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How come you're getting so heated up\N{\c&He1e1e1&}over a lousy game of cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Geez, you're so infantile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not, especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What? Are you trying to run me down\N{\c&He1e1e1&}because I've lost 97 hands in a row?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You know, we're just\N{\c&He1e1e1&}killing time here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I just remembered, I still need\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to take care of some of my bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Quitting while you're ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Take him down in one shot,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Silver! Let him have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Drag him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to knock you off of that\N{\c&He1e1e1&}arrogant perch of yours right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You'll have to put this arm in a splint!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't go running back home down\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the track tube after you've lost to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What happens here, stays here, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You can tell that to your futon\N{\c&He1e1e1&}when we get to the hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Would you like some of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the local {\i1}Kamameshi{\i0} stew?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now {\i1}that{\i0} is traveling cuisine for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How about some {\i1}takekama{\i0} paste\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to go with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What time are you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Would you like some moray pie\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to go with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If it's okay with you,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}how about getting together later?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Would you like some wasabi\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to go with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}These cards are cursed!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}112 losses in a row is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}--My word...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--What are these,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...for her to be this frustrated...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--the cards that led\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to Napoleon's ruin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...is rather refreshing.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--For crying out loud!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun!{\i0} You sucked\N{\c&He1e1e1&}all of my luck out of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and called up some kind\N{\c&He1e1e1&}of evil force, didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're having a bit\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}too{\i0} good a time, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Would you be quiet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Give a little thought\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to the people around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Do you want to get\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the SDF called on you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Uh... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What the? This hand is too weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Good grief, young people these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We will soon be arriving\N{\c&He1e1e1&}at our final destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}the 26th planet, Robunte Roldo.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}This is Robunte Roldo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...that's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Maybe I ought to burn these cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-kun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This looks like a pretty nice place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Y- yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Murase Inn"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I should have known your parents' home\N{\c&He1e1e1&}would be so nice, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Being old is its only merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, is there an open-air bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hmm? You've got that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Welcome! So glad you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you for always\N{\c&He1e1e1&}putting up with our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You must be tired\N{\c&He1e1e1&}after your long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}--Thank you for having us.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--Thank you for having us.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--Thank you for having us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Well, be my guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, everyone, come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What are you doing, {\i1}Yuuki-kun?{\i0} Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, is there an open-air bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, any open-air...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, Shirobota! I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You haven't changed at all.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Unlike my aging mom and pop, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What kind of child compares\N{\c&He1e1e1&}his parents to the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That smart-mouth and hefty frame of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}are the only things that have increased\N{\c&He1e1e1&}with age. Who needs a kid like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Keep it up! I was actually going\N{\c&He1e1e1&}easy on you, on account of your old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, is there an open-air bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, right, right.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}You came to greet me, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, is there an open-air bath!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Good thing there is. Otherwise, I'd have\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to dig up the whole mountain out back
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}until a hot spring turned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right! Today,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to our hearts' content...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...we'll play, eat, drink, and sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...and then scrub ourselves\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in the hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Whatever you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}but why do you have to divide\N{\c&He1e1e1&}your sentences up among the three of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Okay, then, first off...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...to the tennis court...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...to work up a little sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Is it okay for me to be doing this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-san,{\i0} let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Y- yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's the big deal with {\i1}Yuuki-kun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Flirting around like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you all right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I- I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}15-Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ready, set... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Game set.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Good game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Good game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ah, I've worked up a sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All righty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I- if you want, you could\N{\c&He1e1e1&}team up with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}--Why not!?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--Why not!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ah, you're so cute every time\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I see you, Shirobota!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How cute you are! What a good kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He's such a graceless boy.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Has he been causing you much trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Have you had your supper yet today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It sure is peaceful, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, you need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I heard about a place where\N{\c&He1e1e1&}there are some girls around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's take a quick bath\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and go spread our wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're spreading them too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, coming to the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Manabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're heading to the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Huh? Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Tora! So this is where you went, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I've been looking for you.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}You really had me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Such a curious thing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Always going off exploring\N{\c&He1e1e1&}whenever we go someplace new.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah? Naughty little boy, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What a rude man, huh Tora?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}She's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Looks to me like you're pretty deficient\N{\c&He1e1e1&}when it comes to the female mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I wouldn't exactly say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Say, {\i1}Louis-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How are you actually getting along?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Getting along?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't play dumb. With {\i1}Yuuki-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're just friends who joined the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}force at the same time, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}W- what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Then I can more actively\N{\c&He1e1e1&}pursue him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}G- go ahead, feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now, now, don't tease her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain, I was being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Say, Manabu, care to bet\N{\c&He1e1e1&}which one of us can swim underwater
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}to the other side first?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Whoever loses has to perform\N{\c&He1e1e1&}at the banquet tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Yuuki-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're more daring than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You sure had yourself some fun,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}huh Manabu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It wasn't, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Perhaps not, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This fresh snow here... Don't you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}want to leave something in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right, let's make snow-silhouettes!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Jump up, and go spread-eagle in midair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you say you're going to do it,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}then I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It'll look better if\N{\c&He1e1e1&}there are two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Eh? Me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The order of your superior\N{\c&He1e1e1&}is the voice of God. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Splat"? D- David?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:12:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I- it seems to have\N{\c&He1e1e1&}become a slab of ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Nope. It's rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you serious!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you all right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He is a member of the SDF. He is\N{\c&He1e1e1&}prepared to meet with a tragic end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Louis-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Perhaps it's none of my business,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}but you should tell him\N{\c&He1e1e1&}your feelings soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}B- but, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If I've got it all wrong, I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}but timing is important.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Especially to men who are so dim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Just feeling it in your heart\N{\c&He1e1e1&}won't get anything done. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}when you feel the time is right,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I hope you'll gather up your courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and tell him what you honestly feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I- if you want, you could team up...\N{\c&He1e1e1&}team up with... team up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Not even if the planet was being\N{\c&He1e1e1&}swallowed up by the sun with me on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}--Why not!?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--Why not!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"SDF Party"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"SDF Party"\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Yo! I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This will be my last night on Mt. Akagi,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}as well as with you, my dear companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I must take my leave of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}♪ I will be sure to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}return to you someday. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}--Olé!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--Olé!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}♪ People, no matter who they are,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}as they pursue their dreams, ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}♪ have the courage\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to travel new paths... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.24,0:14:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's the matter? Why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I just can't seem to settle in.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Isn't anyone else concerned about work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}While we're all here now,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}there could be something happening
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}on the Galaxy Railways'\N{\c&He1e1e1&}tracks somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There's a nice view here, huh Manabu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The air is good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You can't even see your breath.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}The air is too fair for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're right. Even as cold as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Awesome! That's a first for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You should enjoy times like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, are you enjoying yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Can't you tell by looking at my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah, well, I wouldn't exactly\N{\c&He1e1e1&}call it a very happy face...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Er, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Well, that {\i1}is{\i0} the opinion\N{\c&He1e1e1&}most people have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ah! I thought I was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I like it. This is a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}To me, this is the most\N{\c&He1e1e1&}boring planet in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah. That's why I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you like it, how about living here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}On the most boring planet\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You don't have to answer right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm talking about once you've\N{\c&He1e1e1&}become more of an older woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}More?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That makes it sound like\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm already an older woman now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Lay off! It was a slip of the tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is awful! This is awful!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What's the matter!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Tora... Tora has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I don't know! Once I realized it,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}she was nowhere around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}With all this snow!? If she\N{\c&He1e1e1&}went outside and got lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}--SDF, scramble!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--SDF, scramble!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--SDF, scramble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Torch check!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Torch check, standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Portable communicator systems normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Standing by for search scope parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All equipment, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Straw coats, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Straw boots and snowshoes, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius Platoon, Vega Platoon,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}move to launch position!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius Platoon, ready to move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Vega Platoon, ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All platoons,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}standby at current positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Um... Bruce?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Those who are in the SDF must be\N{\c&He1e1e1&}prepared to handle any situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}R- right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You guys... are SDF!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius Platoon, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Vega Platoon, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Tora seems to have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Tora-chan{\i0} was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}...in the open-air bath with Shirobota.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}--What did you say!?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--What did you say!?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Tora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is the matter, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuki, have you been\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in here the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes. It felt so good,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Together with these little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Even though they are cats,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}they seem to love taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No, don't look, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey, out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Now I'm wide awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Well, might as well\N{\c&He1e1e1&}take another dip now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Once we get warmed up,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}how about we have another banquet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But before we do that, how about\N{\c&He1e1e1&}we all do some mixed bathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Um... Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Old Ravine"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Old Ravine"\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Ryusaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Have you forgotten to say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I said thanks. Everyone was\N{\c&He1e1e1&}able to relax, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, that! That won't come until later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Anyhow, go on living a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That girl would look good\N{\c&He1e1e1&}as his wife, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah. She's too good for that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Tora, have a happy life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Okay, if you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Here we go, everyone! Show us your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Where is it we'll be\N{\c&He1e1e1&}returning to after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}--{\i1}Desti-nee!{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--{\i1}Desti-nee!{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}--{\i1}Desti-nee!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}A momentary respite...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Everyone wishes they could leave{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}themselves to such a place forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}However,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}it is never something{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}that lasts for very long.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}How many nights have{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I spent alone since then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:22:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Constantly having dreams of the hope{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}that you are, as I lightly sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The smiles and tears{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}that you gave to me and me alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}come to mind every time{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}I get disheartened,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}and I set forth again toward the morrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The joyful light of the galaxy beckons me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to that beloved person within my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.56,0:22:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}No matter how far apart we are,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}my memories will never fade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:23:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}My heart wishes always{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}to be at your side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Next Time"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}SPG... Space Panzer Grenadiers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.93,0:23:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}The elite unit that my brother,{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Mamoru, was in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.27,0:23:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Their harsh training is getting underway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Next time on Tales of the{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Galaxy Railways, Episode 20:{\i0} "Choices"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}We're going to encounter{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}something at the next station.{\i0}